of lighter fluid

00:04:12.100 --> 00:04:14.920
but your barbecue charcoal
is still taking too long to light

00:04:15.100 --> 00:04:16.020
Shorten your prep time

00:04:16.020 --> 00:04:18.020
by using the blower function
on a shopvac,

00:04:18.300 --> 00:04:19.170
a hair dryer

00:04:19.170 --> 00:04:20.920
or if you don't have electricity

00:04:21.050 --> 00:04:22.320
a simple balloon pump.

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:25.170
These balloon pumps are great
because they work as a bellows

00:04:25.170 --> 00:04:27.870
that push air out on both 
the pull and the push.

